# Config Topology

| File | Committed | Purpose |
|------|-----------|---------|
| `boske-production.example.json` | Yes | Schema template with placeholder hosts |
| `boske-production.json` | No (gitignored) | Operator local topology |

## Schema sections

- `discovery` — Coolify/Hetzner auto-discovery settings
- `serverOverlays` — roles, health URLs, manual stacks, private probes
- `servers` — static server entries
- `coolify` / `alerts` / `polling` — integration and timing config

## Rules

- Example file must use placeholder URLs (e.g. `example.dev`) and fake IPs.
- Never embed API tokens — tokens go in Keychain via Settings.
- When extending schema, update both example JSON and `Models.swift` in core.
- Add `ConfigLoaderTests` coverage for new config fields.
